title: Cuomo digs in, Chaos in the skies, and Evictions delayed... perhaps
summary:
Guest host George Conway (and a pack of dogs) join Kara to unpack the results of a special election, new information on Trump's last days in office, and the damning report on Governor Andrew Cuomo. Also, could a class action lawsuit make Facebook the new Big Tobacco?
